longBusinessSummary: Cyberlux Corporation designs, develops, and markets portable lighting products for commercial and industrial users in the United States. The company offers BrightEye tactical illumination systems and related products that address the lighting needs of various branches of the military and government organization, including the National Guard, the U. S. Air Force, and the U.S. Army. It serves the Department of Defense/military markets, as well as Homeland Security customers. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Durham, North Carolina.
